on":5,"name":"AI Photo Editor","item":"/products/firefly/features/ai-photo-editor/"}]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/UniversalNav.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/layout.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/popover.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/profile.bundle.css"><link rel="preload" as="script" crossorigin="anonymous" href="/libs/blocks/aside/aside.js"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/aside/aside.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/features/icons/icons.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/creativecloud/blocks/firefly-howto/firefly-howto.css"><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"How to edit photos using the Firefly AI photo editor.","description":"Steps on how to edit photos using the Firefly AI photo editor","step":[{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 1 Open Firefly to access Quick Actions and edit photos with AI.","text":"To get started, log in to Adobe Firefly with your Adobe ID or create a free account if you don’t have one. Browse features and Quick Actions to edit your photo or open the Prompt to Edit feature directly in Firefly."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 2 Upload a photo.","text":"In the Image module, you can either choose a previously generated image from the Generate tab, or click the Edit tab to upload your own images."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 3 Choose an AI model.","text":"Select an image generator model from the dropdown menu in the prompt field. You can choose the Firefly image model, or partner models from Google, OpenAI, and more."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 4 Write a text prompt.","text":"Type a clear description of what you’d like to change directly into the prompt field. Start with at least five words for the best results, for example, “remove the power lines from the sky” or “add warm sunlight and a soft glow.” You can include specific keywords like “vintage look,” “realistic lighting,” or “studio background” to the AI photo editor toward your desired style."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 5 Review edited results.","text":"Click Generate and wait as Firefly edits your image in seconds."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 6 Refine, edit, regenerate.","text":"Refine your image by tweaking the prompt or adjusting the settings for a fresh result. Use one of the additional AI photo editor features in Firefly like Generative Remove, Generative Expand, or Generative Upscale to expand your creativity."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 7 Download and share.","text":"Once you’re satisfied with your creation, you can download it, copy it to your clipboard, or share it directly with others. Turn your AI-edited photo into eye-catching social posts, videos, flyers, and more."}],"totalTime":"PT5M","tool":[{"@type":"HowToTool","name":"firefly"}]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/editorial-card/editorial-card.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/styles/rounded-corners.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/creativecloud/blocks/firefly-carousel/firefly-carousel.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/accordion/accordion.css"><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[[{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              What is an AI photo editor?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"An AI photo editor uses artificial intelligence to simplify image editing and enhancement. With Adobe Firefly, you can upload or generate an image, then use intuitive prompts to remove objects, adjust lighting, change backgrounds, or refine color and composition easily.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              What is the best AI photo editor?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"The best AI photo editor enables users to quickly and easily make major transformations and quick edits, such as replacing a background or retouching the fine details of an image, with high-quality results. The Adobe Firefly AI photo editor is a strong choice for achieving such results without sacrificing creative control.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Do I need design skills to use an AI photo editor?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"The Firefly AI image editor is built for everyone, so you can make professional-quality edits using simple text prompts without advanced photo editing skills.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Can I use Firefly photo editor capabilities on mobile devices?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Adobe Firefly works seamlessly across devices, so you can create and edit on desktop, mobile, or tablet, whether you’re using Mac, Windows, iOS, or Android. Start refining images on your laptop, then switch to your phone or tablet to keep editing on the go.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              What types of photo edits can I make with AI?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"With Adobe Firefly, you can:","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Which AI photo editor gives natural results?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Adobe Firefly is built for realism and professional-grade quality. Its models are trained on licensed content to produce commercially safe, natural-looking edits that blend seamlessly into your images.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Which AI photo editor is best for beginners?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Adobe Firefly is ideal for beginners thanks to its easy-to-use interface and simple text-based editing. You can start creating right away, experiment freely, and refine results without advanced photo editing experience.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Is the Adobe Firefly AI photo editor free to use?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Yes, you can use the Prompt to Edit feature in Firefly for free ai photo editor capabilities with a Firefly Free plan. Free users receive a set number of limited monthly generative credits for both standard and premium features, and a paid subscription is not required.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Is the Firefly AI photo editor safe for commercial use?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Firefly generative AI models are commercially safe. The Adobe Firefly generative AI models were trained on licensed content, such as Adobe Stock, and public domain content where copyright has expired. For partner models, you are responsible for determining whether the model is appropriate for your project.","@type":"Answer"}}]]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="/creativecloud/blocks/firefly-share/firefly-share.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/global-navigation/utilities/menu/menu.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/styles/inline.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/global-footer/global-footer.css"></head>
