      <div class="section" daa-lh="s12">
        <div class="accordion-container seo max-width-12-desktop con-block" data-block-status="loaded" daa-lh="b1|accordion-conta"><div class="descr-list accordion foreground" id="accordion-1" role="presentation"><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-1" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-1" daa-ll="open-1--What is an AI photo ">
            
              What is an AI photo editor?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-1" id="accordion-1-content-1" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>An AI photo editor uses artificial intelligence to simplify image editing and enhancement. With Adobe Firefly, you can upload or generate an image, then use intuitive prompts to remove objects, adjust lighting, change backgrounds, or refine color and composition easily.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-2" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-2" daa-ll="open-2--What is the best AI ">
            
              What is the best AI photo editor?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-2" id="accordion-1-content-2" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>The best AI photo editor enables users to quickly and easily make major transformations and quick edits, such as replacing a background or retouching the fine details of an image, with high-quality results. The Adobe Firefly AI photo editor is a strong choice for achieving such results without sacrificing creative control.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-3" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-3" daa-ll="open-3--Do I need design ski">
            
              Do I need design skills to use an AI photo editor?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-3" id="accordion-1-content-3" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>The Firefly AI image editor is built for everyone, so you can make professional-quality edits using simple text prompts without advanced photo editing skills.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-4" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-4" daa-ll="open-4--Can I use Firefly ph">
            
              Can I use Firefly photo editor capabilities on mobile devices?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-4" id="accordion-1-content-4" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>
              <p>Adobe Firefly works seamlessly across devices, so you can create and edit on desktop, mobile, or tablet, whether you’re using Mac, Windows, iOS, or Android. Start refining images on your laptop, then switch to your phone or tablet to keep editing on the go.</p>
              <p>Projects sync automatically through Creative Cloud, making it easy to collaborate with teammates or clients and maintain a consistent workflow across platforms. Firefly also supports style transfers and other creative effects, so you can match looks or themes between devices without losing quality or context.</p>
            </div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-5" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-5" daa-ll="open-5--What types of photo ">
            
              What types of photo edits can I make with AI?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-5" id="accordion-1-content-5" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>
              <p>With Adobe Firefly, you can:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Use Prompt to Edit to add, remove, or replace objects and backgrounds.</li>
                <li>Clean up images with Generative Fill to remove unwanted elements.</li>
                <li>Transform photos into new styles or moods using image-to-image editing.</li>
              </ul>
              <p>The AI photo editor gives you flexible tools to enhance, reimagine, and perfect any image.</p>
            </div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-6" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-6" daa-ll="open-6--Which AI photo edito">
            
              Which AI photo editor gives natural results?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-6" id="accordion-1-content-6" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Adobe Firefly is built for realism and professional-grade quality. Its models are trained on licensed content to produce commercially safe, natural-looking edits that blend seamlessly into your images.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-7" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-7" daa-ll="open-7--Which AI photo edito">
            
              Which AI photo editor is best for beginners?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-7" id="accordion-1-content-7" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Adobe Firefly is ideal for beginners thanks to its easy-to-use interface and simple text-based editing. You can start creating right away, experiment freely, and refine results without advanced photo editing experience.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-8" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-8" daa-ll="open-8--Is the Adobe Firefly">
            
              Is the Adobe Firefly AI photo editor free to use?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-8" id="accordion-1-content-8" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, you can use the Prompt to Edit feature in Firefly for free ai photo editor capabilities with a Firefly Free plan. Free users receive a set number of limited monthly generative credits for both standard and premium features, and a paid subscription is not required.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-9" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-9" daa-ll="open-9--Is the Firefly AI ph">
            
              Is the Firefly AI photo editor safe for commercial use?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-9" id="accordion-1-content-9" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Firefly generative AI models are commercially safe. The Adobe Firefly generative AI models were trained on licensed content, such as Adobe Stock, and public domain content where copyright has expired. For partner models, you are responsible for determining whether the model is appropriate for your project.</div></div></div></div>
      </div>
